Package: autoclick
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip, libxcb-cursor0, libxkbcommon-x11-0
Maintainer: CrisTecnica <cristecnica@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: AutoClick - Desktop macro recorder
 AutoClick is a desktop macro recorder and player for Linux (X11).
 It captures mouse and keyboard events globally and replays them
 with adjustable speed, infinite loop support, and global hotkeys.
 .
 Features:
  - Mouse and keyboard event recording
  - Adjustable playback speed (0.1x to 10x)
  - Infinite loop mode
  - Global hotkeys (F9-F12, Esc)
  - Event editor with reorder/delete/duplicate
  - JSON save/load
  - Dark theme UI
  - System tray support
Homepage: https://github.com/CrisTecnica/autoclick
